title: Newly Renovated 3 Bed/3 Bath + Den/Office - Panoramic Views !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
